  <trk>
    <name>306 Rinderberg - Hornberg - Horneggli</name>
    <desc><![CDATA[The easier high-altitude hike impresses with a magnificent Alpine panorama and is also suitable for families and seniors. / Along the entire route, there is a fascinating view of the distinctive Simmen Valley and Saanenland mountain world with the Wildstrubel, the Rüebli, or the Gummfluh as well as the massif of the northern Alpine chain. ]]></desc>
